        "front": "What is a chord progression?",
        "back": "A chord progression is a sequence of chords played in a piece of music.",
        "icon": "🎶"
      },
      {
        "front": "Why are chord progressions important?",
        "back": "They form the foundation of songs and help create harmony.",
        "icon": "🎸"
      },
      {
        "front": "What is a common chord progression for beginners?",
        "back": "The I-IV-V progression is popular and easy to play.",
        "icon": "📖"
      },
      {
        "front": "How can you practice chord progressions?",
        "back": "Practice slowly, focus on smooth transitions, and use a metronome.",
        "icon": "🕒"
      }
    ]
  }
}
